channel.title: Extending the Object List?
channel.description:
Anyone know how to extend the object list? Because I added the bounty hunter object map and I have the objects hardcoded in. When I compile I get no errors, but when it tries to load them I get an outofbounds exception. So, I'm pretty sure if I extend my object list it'll fix this problem. If anyone knows how please tell me.
Thanks, Moose[br][br][size=1]Posted on: November 22, 2009, 04:08:50 pm[/size][hr]No one knows how to do this? I figured a lot of people already had extended their object lists...
